- **enable**: enables K8s Service-based service registration and discovery.', example='{"serviceName":"bwm-poc-sc-gateway-cn-beijing-front","namespaceId":"cn-beijing:front","portAndProtocol":{"18012":"TCP"},"enable":true,"portProtocols":[{"port":18012,"protocol":"TCP"}]}'),
  python?: string(name='Python', description='The Python environment. **PYTHON 3.9.15** is supported.', example='PYTHON 3.9.15'),
